{"type":"message","id":"320275d9","parentId":"3d4b74e7","timestamp":"2026-05-29T02:30:03.989Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is frustrated that the conversation history is empty. They're asking why it's empty and whether I store conversation history.\n\nLooking at the memory search results, I can see references to past conversations from May 10, 12, 13, 14 about the Feishu bitable write permissions and sorftime API issues. But the LCM conversation is empty for the current session - which means this is the same session but lossless-claw conversation was not found.\n\nWait, actually looking at the runtime info: `sessionKey=agent:tts:feishu:tts:direct:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68`. And the error says \"No LCM conversation found for this session\" - this suggests LCM (Lossless Context Management) hasn't stored any conversation for this session.\n \nSo the issue is that this is the current session but LCM is showing empty for it. The memory search does show some history from earlier sessions through semantic memory, but the current conversation itself isn't being persisted - which aligns with what the user is experiencing. I need to explain what's happening with the memory system and why this session appears empty despite having historical context available.\n","thinkingSignature":"008ade05e16aa1a95793de953d8137bf33365c947e03957f3623ea8aa479c62a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n会话确实空了——Lossless-Claw 没有找到这次对话的存储记录，所以上下文是空的。\n\n不过我通过**语义记忆**找到了之前的内容。你提到\"又失败了\"，根据之前记录，问题是**飞书多维表写入被拒**——需要把 bot 加为多维表协作者并给「可编辑」权限。\n\n这个多维表：https://bytedance.feishu.cn/base/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\n\n之前我们来回折腾了好几次权限的事。你在多维表里把 `TK选品大师`（或 bot 名）加进去并给「可编辑」权限了吗？\n\n上次失败的具体原因是什么——是 sorftime 查询失败了，还是写入多维表被拒？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5028,"output":413,"cacheRead":43450,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48891,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopRe